These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, almond-milk, water, 7up, hot-chocolate, juice
There are 7 different favourite colors: amber, grey, orange, coral, lilac, ebony, chestnut
 1. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking water and the person drinking juice##2
 2. the person drinking tea is in the middle##1
 3. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is between the person who likes orange and the person who likes lilac##2
 5. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
 6. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 7. the person who likes amber is between the person who likes coral and the person who likes orange##2
 8. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | water | sprite | juice | tea    | almond-milk | 7up   | hot-chocolate    |
| Color         | ebony  | grey   | coral | amber | orange   | chestnut | lilac |

