.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: dubstep, rock, reggae, funk, gospel, disco, hip-hop
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: poppy, daisy, iris, marigold, dahlia, rose, orchid
1. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1
2. the fan reggae is between the fan disco and the person who growsrose##2
3. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
4. the fan hip-hop is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
5. the fan rock is in the middle##1
6. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
7. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the fan rock##1
8. the fan gospel is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
9. the fan funk is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Music-Genre          | gospel | reggae | disco | rock | hip-hop | dubstep      | funk  |
| Flower   | rose | marigold  | orchid     | iris     | dahlia  | poppy | daisy |

