.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: folk, metal, country, reggae, jazz, dubstep, disco
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: lacrosse, handball, skiing, swimming, ice-hockey, soccer, rugby
 1. the fan jazz is on the left of the fan folk##1
 2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the fan disco##1
 4. the fan country is on the left of the fan dubstep##1
 5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 6. the fan reggae is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the fan folk is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person who's sport is rugby and the fan reggae##2
 9. the fan folk is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
10. the fan metal is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | disco | jazz | folk | metal   | reggae | country | dubstep |
| Sport           | ice-hockey | soccer     | handball     | skiing | swimming   | lacrosse   | rugby    |

