.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There 7 different types of food: onion, raspberry, cherry, carrot, potato, avocado, cranberry
There are 7 different favourite colors: orange, green, amber, black, emerald, azure, yellow
 1. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
 2. the person eating potato is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
 3. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes black##1
 4. the person eating potato is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
 5. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person eating onion##1
 6. the person who likes black is between the person eating cherry and the person who likes azure##2
 7. the person eating onion is in the middle##1
 8. the person who likes black is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
 9. the person eating raspberry is the person who likes green##1
10. the person who likes orange is the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Food      | cherry    | potato  | carrot  | onion  | cranberry      | avocado       | raspberry |
| Color   | emerald | black | azure | yellow | orange | amber | green  |

