.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
There 7 different types of food: cucumber, zucchini, kale, banana, carrot, lemon, grapefruit
House: victorian, cape-cod, ranch-style, craftsman, gothic-revival, tower, cottage
1. the craftsman house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
2. the gothic-revival house is the person eating zucchini##1
3. the victorian house is between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating cucumber##2
4. the person eating lemon is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
5. the victorian house is in the middle##1
6. the tower house is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
7. the ranch-style house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
8. the cape-cod house is the person eating banana##1
9. the person eating carrot is the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Food   | banana      | carrot | cucumber | kale | grapefruit      | zucchini      | lemon |
| House     | cape-cod | tower | cottage       | victorian | ranch-style | gothic-revival | craftsman |

