.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
7 different pets are kept: rabbit, frog, rat, hamster, dog, bird, horse
The people use 7 different means of transport: motorbike, van, bike, boat, taxi, trike, ship
1. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the person driving the bike is the owner of the dog##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
6. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the taxi and the owner of the rabbit##2
7. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the van##1
8. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Pet     | dog | rabbit | hamster | bird | frog | rat     | horse |
| Transport   | bike   | boat    | ship    | taxi      | van  | motorbike | trike |

