 7. the person who growsazalea is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 8. the person who growsmarigold is the person who growsmarigold##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
10. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |     3     |       4       |      5      |    6     |    7     |
